

### AU-S1: Login Success (Active User)
POST {{baseUrlForAuth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "superadmin@warehouse.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### AU-F1: Login Failure (Incorrect Credentials) # Logic: Service catches AuthenticationException

POST {{baseUrlForAuth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "superadmin@warehouse.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### AU-F2: Login Failure (Inactive Account) # Logic: Service checks UserStatus.ACTIVE enum

POST {{baseUrlForAuth}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "inactive_user@infotact.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### AU-S2: Forgot Password Request
POST {{baseUrlForAuth}}/forgot-password?email=superadmin@warehouse.com

### AU-F3: Reset Password (Invalid/Expired Token)
POST {{baseUrlForAuth}}/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "invalid-uuid-token",
    "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword@123"
}